---
title: Creamy Garlic Salmon Penne with Spinach and Parmesan
description: This one's for those garlic lovers out there! Flaked salmon stirred through with spinach and finished with Parmesan is decadent and perfect for a memorable dinner!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pennes-a-la-sauce-cremeuse-a-lail-et-au-saumon-91817fc8.jpg
